metadata.name: INKomplete #001
metadata.description:
Trying to get an idea of who or what a person is, from a distance, is easy. It gives us a rough idea, but the closer we get, the more we realize how complex a person is and how all this complexity is made out of the same simple set of traits and how their unique combinations, Define each person, differently.

This makes us realize that what we think we know, is always : INKomplete.
